      /**

big ML table of best model fit for subj vs. obj prob

based on:
*By Phil Tian (week10, task7)

@author Markus Schaffner

*/

clear all
set more off

cd "/Users/mas/Dropbox/EXPERIMENTS/OET/material"

cap log close
log using "log/table3_bigOLS.smcl", replace smcl

use "dta/oet_data_ready.dta"

/*
set more off 

estimates drop _all

// cd C:
cd /Users/schaffne/Dropbox/OET
use "oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta", clear

do oet_first_paper/do/varsets.do
*/

gen winpc2 = winpc^2
gen winpc3 = winpc^3

reg pse winpc $minimal, cluster(subjectid)
estimates store m1, title (Spec 1-a)

reg pse winpc $minimal $exp, cluster(subjectid)
estimates store m2, title (Spec 2-a)

reg pse winpc $minimal $exp $demo $edu, cluster(subjectid)
estimates store m3, title (Spec 3-a)

reg pse winpc $minimal $exp $demo $edu $psych $physio, cluster(subjectid)
estimates store m4, title (Spec 4-a)

cap program drop OET_ML
program define OET_ML
args lnf k sigma
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`k')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end


ml model lf OET_ML (k: pse = winpc $minimal $exp $demo $edu $psych $physio ) (sigma: winpc $minimal $exp $demo $edu $psych $physio)
ml maximize, difficult
estimates store m5

estout m1 m2 m3 m4 m5 

// using oet_first_paper/tables/bigOLS.tex, style(tex)
estout m1 m2 m3 m4 m5 using  "tables/table3_bigOLS.tex", style(tex)  ///
    replace unstack ///
   mlabels(,nodepvars notitle none) eqlabels(, none) ///
   cells( "b(fmt(%9.3fc) star vacant(&) ) se(fmt(%9.3fc) par)" ) ///
   label drop(_cons) ///
   collabels(none) ///
   stats(F p N r2_a ll, fmt(%9.3f %9.3f %9.0f %9.3f %9.2f) labels("\$F$" "\$Pr()>F$" "\$N$" "\$Adj. R^2$" "\$ll$")  layout( \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} )) ///
   prefoot("\hline") ///
   starlevels("&" 1.00 "&*" 0.10 "&**" 0.05 "&***" 0.01)

estout * ,cells(b(star))

log close

// eof
